Subject: [PATCH 0226/1239] arm64: mvebu: dts: a37xx: add DDR4 db-C rev 3.x dts

This patch added dts support for DDR4 with rev 3.x ECO.
Config "C" dts configurates comphy0 with sgmii1-sfp2.5g.

Change-Id: I7766739b112f0fe09735157b419670758c298e0c
Signed-off-by: Stefan Chulski <stefanc@marvell.com>
